      <text xml:space="preserve">{{Refimprove|date=April 2010}}
{{Infobox scientist
|name              =Christian Doppler
|image             =Christian Doppler.jpg
|image_width       =
|nationality       = [[Austria]]n
|birth_date        = {{Birth date|1803|11|29|df=yes}}
