|- 
|  style=&quot;background:#{{LUL color|District}}; width:20px;&quot;| || [[Sutton, London|Sutton]] – [[Tooting]] || Through [[St. Helier, London|St Helier]] and [[Mitcham]] (including routing variants via [[Mitcham Junction]] and direct)
