|-
|  style=&quot;background:#{{LUL color|Hammersmith &amp; City}}; width:20px;&quot;| || [[Beckenham Junction station|Harrington Road/Beckenham Junction]] – [[Crystal Palace, London|Crystal Palace]] || Various route options including (below)
|}
 
